name: Search component
description:
A search module with different layout and components:

· Buttons
· Input fields
· Drop-down
· Spinners
· Checkboxes
· Tags
· Icons
· Styles

Use this file to add a visual search module to your product or website. Everything is reusable and designed with auto-layout to make different combinations and setups easy to create.

Please DM me on @ikerffernandez if you have any feedback :) 🙏
